{"tid":1737803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"痛定思痛，回歸初心，重整軍勢，繼續行動！","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:37:30.000Z","uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"979e9817964601209f305076d4db0acbdd12e51e","tid":1737803,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"失敗原因出面好多PO講咗，我唔多講，我只係想講<span style=\"color: red;\">如何應對失敗</span>！各位要明白︰<br />\n- 世上無每戰皆勝之軍，只有<span style=\"color: red;\">百戰不殆之軍</span>！<br />\n- 失敗並不可怕，可怕的是放棄！<br />\n- 最緊要<span style=\"color: red;\">敗而不亂，敗而益勇</span>！<br />\n<br />\n日後行動心態︰<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不以成敗論英雄</span><br />\n行動成功或者失敗，都對抗爭有好處。成功的話，搵到抗爭突破位。失敗的話，<span style=\"color: red;\">吸取教訓，避免再犯</span>。只要有出過力嘅人，都係手足，都係英雄！<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只檢討失敗原因，不指責造成失敗之人</span><br />\n成功係所有人都享有榮耀，<span style=\"color: red;\">失敗係所有人都要承擔責任</span>。咁先係有福同享，有難同當！<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回歸初心，攬炒+快閃</span><br />\n星期一至五黎明行動+快閃和你lunch，星期六日商場攬炒，呢個係不敗之地！<br />\n<br />\n借手足之圖一用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbWVycE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbWVycE.jpg&h=ca3d6b0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2189e5b186138d1b5df717b00ecf6294eb178d56","tid":1737803,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:06:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入-----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=c860787a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"38e8e6dc302c2267a42db1a2dd90b76c1a7bf01e","tid":1737803,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g